            <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1291291" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1644335 - prov 4" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1644991" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Section 4</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="789653" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1644991" atidlm:targetKey="883930" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM158592" atidlm:targetName="prov 4" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1644991" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM158588.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1130900.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1130942" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> is amended by adding the following subsections:</text>
            <amend quote="1">
              <subprov quote="1" skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">3</label>
                <para>
                  <text>A person is an <def-term id="DLM1131069">associated person</def-term> in relation to 1 or more other persons if—</text>
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>each person is a body corporate and each of the bodies corporate—</text>
                      <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>consist substantially of the same members or shareholders; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>are under the control of the same persons; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>any of the bodies corporate—</text>
                      <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>has the power, directly or indirectly, to exercise, or control the exercise of, 25% or more of the voting power at a meeting of the other; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>is able to appoint or control 25% or more of the governing body of the other.</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </subprov>
              <subprov quote="1" skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">4</label>
                <para>
                  <text>For the purposes of the definition of dispose, a deposit of waste is short-term if, not later than 6 months after the deposit (or any later time that the chief executive has agreed to in writing), the waste is—</text>
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>reused or recycled; or</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>recovered; or</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">c</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>removed from the land for any other reason.</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </subprov>
              <subprov quote="1" skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">5</label>
                <para>
                  <text>Pre-1990 forest land, in respect of which conversion to land that is not forest land had commenced prior to <citation jurisdiction="nz">31 December 2007</citation>, is to be treated as deforested on <citation jurisdiction="nz">31 December 2007</citation> if, on that date, the land had—</text>
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>no standing exotic forest species (dead or alive), other than a strip of standing exotic forest species that had, or was likely at maturity to have, tree crown cover of an average width of less than 30 metres; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>no other merchantable timber from exotic forest species.</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </subprov>
            </amend>
          </para>
        </subprov>
      </prov.body>
    </prov>
    <prov id="DLM1131070" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">7</label>
      <heading>Minister of Finance may give directions to Registrar regarding accounts and units</heading>
      <prov.body>
        <subprov skeleton="no">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
          <para>
            <text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1291292" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1644336 - prov 7" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1644992" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Section 7(1)(a)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="789654" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1644992" atidlm:targetKey="884801" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM159524" atidlm:targetName="prov 7" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1644992" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM159522.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1130900.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1131070" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> is amended by adding the following subparagraphs:</text>
